at the Crawford house?

05:56.540 --> 05:58.531
-No.
-Did he know the Crawfords?

05:58.540 --> 06:00.076
If he does, he's not saying.

06:00.080 --> 06:02.207
In fact, he hasn't said a word
since his arrest.

06:02.790 --> 06:05.111
