you wanna ask me, boy,

08:19.920 --> 08:21.820
you look me in the eye and you ask.

08:29.120 --> 08:32.112
-Three days ago...
-You're not looking at me.

08:37.880 --> 08:40.667
Three days ago,
the Crawford family was murdered.

08:40.670 --> 08:42.376
Is that right?

08:42.830 --> 08:45.378
-Did you know them

08:50.380 --> 08:53.668
