maybe the car was just an attempt

12:09.040 --> 12:11.998
-to show the other parents wealth.
-Like this house.

12:13.380 --> 12:15.701
Designer magazines
conspicuously placed.

12:15.710 --> 12:19.077
Expensive modern furniture.
Plasma TV.

12:20.170 --> 12:22.286
Behind the curtains, water damage.

12:22.290 --> 12:24.827
