16:15.880 --> 16:18.451
Mom, Dad, two children out front
holding hands.

16:18.460 --> 16:20.030
And a big dog.

16:20.040 --> 16:22.417
I think this is the Crawford house,
it's signed by Emily.

16:22.420 --> 16:23.489
Strange.

16:23.500 --> 16:26.162
Eric Miller said he found his son
clutching a painting.

16:26.170 --> 16:28.877
-He wanted to know what was on it.
-What was on it?

16:28.880 --> 16:30.370
His son's blood.

16:42.080 --> 16:44.412
Whoa, whoa. Hotch! Hotch!

16:46.750 --> 16:49.457
Hey, whoa, whoa, easy...

16:52.750 --> 16:53.739
Freeze!

17:08.080 --> 17:10.321
