17:11.670 --> 17:13.069
That's mine.

17:13.080 --> 17:17.369
The colors indicate a self-confidence
With an outgorng personality.

17:17.380 --> 17:19.245
It shows an above-average intelligence.

17:19.880 --> 17:22.997
The child that painted this
was left-handed.

17:24.540 --> 17:26.872
Emily Crawford was left-handed.

17:27.790 --> 17:30.577
Frank, you're not.

17:31.540 --> 17:33.610
How'd you get the painting, Frank?

