18:22.880 --> 18:24.950
What bad thing did you do?

18:27.960 --> 18:30.372
The rule was,

18:30.380 --> 18:32.780
I was never supposed to go
to the house.

18:32.790 --> 18:34.951
That was the only rule.

18:35.420 --> 18:41.529
Allison said if Chris saw me _
he would never let me see her again.

18:41.880 --> 18:44.417
